{"type": "article", "id": 28724, "title": "自救戒指", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-27T06:51:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 80, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121016HpFNYVz2jeqncoTu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>在初创公司 <a href=\"http://nimb.com/\">NIMB</a> 的设计师眼中，戒指不仅仅被定义为一件饰品，还可以在关键时刻保护用户的安全。公司最近推出的智能戒指 Nimb 中暗藏了一个按钮，发生紧急情况时轻轻一按就会向家人朋友或者是 Nimb 社区发送求救信号，发送后它还会通过震动向用户进行反馈。通过 Nimb 的手机应用，用户可以选择报警范围，比如警察、家人朋友或者是附近的人。Nimb 还可以用来追踪手机，一旦和手机距离过远，戒指会立刻发出震动。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1629204423/nimb-a-smart-ring-that-keeps-you-safe-and-sound\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 115 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121011L7Y08PO2vCXkMhfT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121012CmgeIjZ6VoFzyXQ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75147059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121012gUBV9AHI8XLj3so5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59174312\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121013YOUNdCwmkZQqRhti.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57205882\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}